{
  "stem": "12674.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Murmelstein had resented my father, so he was going to show him who was the boss.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because otherwise, I would never have been in there because none of us were ever there because of [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ram ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know what he did, but he did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "None of us ever got a thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the only-- I put that together myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that is the only way my name would have gotten on there, because my father said so too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my father wouldn't introduce him, so he couldn't have me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ram ?] had said that this family, whichever way, or whenever the list came up to him, he took it out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- I was-- I got a little slip of paper about this big, one inch by, by three inches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it said my name and says report for the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the first thing I did, I went to my father where I knew he was working, and I said, I got this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you stay here, don't move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went to the kommandatur and said to ask for-- and he was let in because he was doing work there all the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they knew him, and he knew others two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The second in command, his father had had a hardware store in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father used to buy from his father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he was a customer of his father's in Vienna, so he knew him too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He used to come sometimes to where my father worked, and they used to share a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he'd still hit people over the head with his oaken stick and killed a few people, but my father was the [NON-ENGLISH] because they knew him from before.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
